#: ../../../user/basics.performant_code.rst:10
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../user/basics.performant_code.rst:12
msgid ""
"NumPy is designed for high performance numerical computing in Python by "
"leveraging vectorized operations. However, vectorization does not always "
"fully utilize the capabilities of multi-core processors. To exploit "
"parallelism, additional strategies are necessary."
msgstr ""

