msgstr ""

#: ../../../user/basics.performant_code.rst:436
msgid ""
"Dask is an open-source library that provides parallel compuing features not "
"only for a single machine but also for a cluster of machines. It also "
"provides ``DaskArray`` which has a similar API to NumPy's ``ndarray``. If "
"you are familiar with NumPy, you can easily get started with ``DaskArray``."
msgstr ""

