#: ../../../user/basics.performant_code.rst:477
msgid ""
"``threadpoolctl`` is a library that provides utilities to control the "
"behavior of thread pools in Python, including other thread pools used by "
"libraries such as BLAS and OpenMP. It allows you to avoid CPU "
"oversubscription when using multiple libraries that utilize threads."
msgstr ""

